{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "velourbe-collection-v1",
    "name": "VeloUrbe API",
    "description": "Colección completa de endpoints para la plataforma de microservicios VeloUrbe.\n\nArquitectura (puertos):\n- Gateway 8080 · Auth 8081 · Rental 8082 · BFF 8083\n- Payment 8084 · Notification 8085 · Analytics 8086\n- Logistics 8087 · Maintenance 8088 · Support 8089\n\nFlujo recomendado:\n1. Login Admin → copiar token → {{token_admin}}\n2. Register / Login Client → copiar token → {{token_client}}\n3. Create Scooter (ADMIN)\n4. Start Rental (CLIENT)\n5. Process Payment / Analytics / Notifications según necesites\n6. End Rental (CLIENT)\n7. BFF Dashboard para ver datos agregados\n\nUsa el environment \"VeloUrbe Local\" o las variables de la colección.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "gateway_url", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "auth_url", "value": "http://localhost:8081", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "rental_url", "value": "http://localhost:8082", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "bff_url", "value": "http://localhost:8083", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "payment_url", "value": "http://localhost:8084", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "notification_url", "value": "http://localhost:8085", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "analytics_url", "value": "http://localhost:8086", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "logistics_url", "value": "http://localhost:8087", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "maintenance_url", "value": "http://localhost:8088", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "support_url", "value": "http://localhost:8089", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token_admin", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token_client", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "user_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "scooter_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "rental_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "payment_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "notification_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "issue_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "ticket_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth Service (8081)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Client",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{auth_url}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{auth_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"cliente@velourbe.cl\",\n  \"password\": \"cliente123\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Juan Pérez\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{auth_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{auth_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@velourbe.cl\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Client",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{auth_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{auth_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"cliente@velourbe.cl\",\n  \"password\": \"cliente123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get All Users (ADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token_admin}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{auth_url}}/api/users", "host": ["{{auth_url}}"], "path": ["api", "users"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token_admin}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{auth_url}}/api/users/{{user_id}}", "host": ["{{auth_url}}"], "path": ["api", "users", "{{user_id}}"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Active Users by Role CLIENT (ADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token_admin}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{auth_url}}/api/users/active/CLIENT", "host": ["{{auth_url}}"], "path": ["api", "users", "active", "CLIENT"] }
          },
          "response": []
